As an artist, you constantly juggle between different roles as the situation demands, which is why I was in search of a laptop that would adapt to all the facets of my life. Thankfully, @dellindia XPS 13 has proven to be the perfect accompaniment. Not only does it combine state-of-the-art features with a sleek and stylish edge, but its powerful technology helps me transition from capturing to creating with ease. Well, this is truly a holy grail for me! What about you?

latestPosts.caption:
#LSAStarmakers: Rahul Jhangiani (@rahuljhangiani) is mastering the art of photography by analyzing emotions, unleashing limitless creativity, and viewing the world differently. Having worked in the industry for years, Jhangiani has had several celebrities playing muse for his lens. His roster of celebrities includes renowned A-listers like Alia Bhatt, The Jonas Brothers, Virat Kohli, to name a few. 

“The beauty of photography lies in its ability to evoke emotions and tell a story. A powerful photograph has the power to connect us, inspire us, and make us see the world in a different way,” he tells us.

Here’s raising a toast to Rahul Jhangiani and his contribution to the field of photography.

Interviewed by Jhanvi Duggal (@jhanvii.23) 

#RahulJhangiani  #Photography
